HEADWORD: Bowsprit
<hw>Bow"sprit`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Bow</ets> +
<ets>sprit</ets>; akin to D. <ets>boegspriet</ets>; <ets>boeg</ets> bow
